    "answer": "(a) 1",
    "explanation": "3*2 = 2(3)+2-(3)(2) = 6+2-6 = 2. 2*1 = 2(2)+1-(2)(1) = 4+1-2 = 3. Now 2*3 = 2(2)+3-(2)(3) = 4+3-6 = 1."
