    "answer": "(a) 5",
    "explanation": "Let notes be x, 2x, 3x. Total value: 10(x) + 20(2x) + 50(3x) = 1000 => 10x + 40x + 150x = 1000 => 200x = 1000 => x = 5. So ₹ 10 notes = 5."
