    "question": "R walks a long distance every Sunday. He walks 2 km towards the north from his house and then turns right; he walks another 2 km and again turns right; next he walks 5 km and turns left; he further walks 2 km and stops. He rests for some time and returns home following a straight route without any turning point. What is the distance R walks after he has rested?",
