    "topic": "Algebra",
    "exam": "CISF 2022",
    "question": "If a > b are two real numbers such that a + b = 10 and a2 + b2 = 52, then what is the value of a-b?",
    "options": [
      "(a) 1",
      "(b) 2",
      "(c) 3",
      "(d) 4"
    ],
    "answer": "(b) 2",
    "explanation": "2ab = (a+b)^2 - (a^2+b^2) = 100 - 52 = 48. (a-b)^2 = (a^2+b^2) - 2ab = 52 - 48 = 4. Since a > b, a-b = 2."
