    "question": "The average age of 5 members of a family is 20 years. The youngest member of the family is 4 years old. Average age of all the members of the family excluding the youngest member is :",
    "options": [
      "(a) 24",
      "(b) 30",
      "(c) 32",
      "(d) 40"
    ],
